<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--

TUMBLR THEME 01: SIMPLE REDIRECT
Code by Pandappuccino

CREDITS:
Cappuccicons Font by Solange Rainha

RULES:
You may edit this code to suit your needs.
You may NOT repost this code or your edits.
You may NOT remove the credit.

A quick and simple redirect page containing an askbox linked to your new page URL. I made this so in the event I decided to change my blog URL I could make a quick redirect page. The theme settings also include a "light mode" toggle, so you can change the box background and credit link colors to light or dark depending on your background.

-->

<html>
    <head>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{Favicon}" />
        <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" href="{RSS}" />
        <title>{Title}</title>
        {block:Description}
        <meta name="description" content="{MetaDescription}" />
        {/block:Description}
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

        <!-- GOOGLE FONTS -->
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family={text:Title Font}:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family={text:Subtitle Font}:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />

        <!-- CAPPUCCICONS -->
        <link href="https://icons.cappuccicons.com/cpf.css" rel="stylesheet" />

        <!-- META TAGS -->
        <meta name="text:Old URL" content="Old URL" />
        <meta name="text:New URL" content="New URL" />

        <meta name="image:Background" content="" />
        <meta name="select:Background Repeat" content="repeat" />
        <meta name="select:Background Repeat" content="repeat-x" />
        <meta name="select:Background Repeat" content="repeat-y" />
        <meta name="select:Background Repeat" content="no-repeat" />

        <meta name="text:Title Font" content="Quintessential" />
        <meta name="text:Subtitle Font" content="Quicksand" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Title Font" content="serif" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Title Font" content="sans-serif" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Title Font" content="monospace" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Subtitle Font" content="serif" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Subtitle Font" content="sans-serif" />
        <meta name="select:Generic Subtitle Font" content="monospace" />

        <meta name="color:Background" content="#232323" />
        <meta name="color:Text" content="#000000" />
        <meta name="color:Link" content="#cdcdcd" />
        <meta name="color:Link Hover" content="#dcdcdc" />

        <meta name="if:Lightmode" content="0" />

        <style>
            @keyframes lazyload {
                        0%   {opacity: 0;}
                        100% {opacity: 1;}
                    }

                    @-webkit-keyframes lazyload {
                        0%   {opacity: 0;}
                        100% {opacity: 1;}
                    }

                    @-moz-keyframes lazyload {
                        0%   {opacity: 0;}
                        100% {opacity: 1;}
                    }

                    @-o-keyframes lazyload {
                        0%   {opacity: 0;}
                        100% {opacity: 1;}
                    }

                body {
                    background-color: {color:Background};
                    background-image: url('{image:Background}');
                    background-repeat: {select:Background Repeat};
                    color: {color:Text};
                    font-family: '{text:Subtitle Font}', {select:Generic Subtitle Font};
                    font-size: 1.25em;
                    text-align: center;
                        -webkit-animation: lazyload 2s;
                        -moz-animation: lazyload 2s;
                        -o-animation: lazyload 2s;
                        animation: lazyload 2s;
                }

                p {
                    padding: 0!important;
                    margin: 0!important;
                }

                a {
                    color: {color:Link};
                    text-decoration: none;
                    transition: all 0.3s;
                }

                a:hover {
                    color: {color:Link Hover};
                }
                
                hr {
                    width: 75%;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                    margin-top: 0;
                    border-color: {color:Link Color};
                }

                #main {
                    width: 60vw;
                    max-width: 750px;
                    min-width:300px;
                    height: auto;
                    margin: 15vh auto;
                    {block:ifLightmode}
                    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
                    box-shadow: 0 0 5px white;
                    {/block:ifLightmode}
                    {block:ifNotLightmode}
                    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
                    box-shadow: 0 0 5px black;
                    {/block:ifNotLightmode}
                    padding: 10px;
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                }

                .oldurl {
                    font-size: 2em;
                }

                .newurl {
                    font-size: 3em;
                    font-family: '{text:Title Font}', {select:Generic Title Font};
                }

                /* DO NOT TOUCH THIS SECTION */
                    #credit {
                        z-index: 9999999;
                        font-size:23px;
                        text-align: center;
                        {block:ifLightmode}
                        color: white;
                        {/block:ifLightmode}
                        {block:ifNotLightmode}
                        color:black;
                        {/block:ifNotLightmode}
                        position: fixed;
                        top: 94%;
                        left: 94%;
                        transition: all 0.2s;
                    }

                    #credit:hover {
                        color: {color:Link Hover};
                    }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div id="main">
            <p class="oldurl">{text:Old URL}</p>
            <p>has relocated to</p>
            <p class="newurl">
                <a href="https://{text:New URL}.tumblr.com">{text:New URL}</a>
            </p>
            <hr>
            <iframe
                frameborder="0"
                scrolling="no"
                width="90%"
                height="300"
                src="https://www.tumblr.com/ask_form/{text:New URL}.tumblr.com"
                style="background-color: transparent; overflow: hidden"
                id="ask_form"
            ></iframe
            ><!--[if IE
                ]><script type="text/javascript">
                    document.getElementById("ask_form").allowTransparency = true;
                </script><!
            [endif]-->
        </div>

        <!-- CREDIT--DO NOT TOUCH!! -->
        <a id="credit" href="https://pandappuccino.tumblr.com" title="Code by Pandappuccino"
            ><i class="cp cp-flower"></i
        ></a>
    </body>
</html>
